# Holiday Configuration File
#
# This file defines holidays when attendance check should be skipped
#
# Format:
#   - Single date: YYYY-MM-DD
#   - Date range:  YYYY-MM-DD~YYYY-MM-DD
#   - Comments:    Lines starting with # are ignored
#   - Empty lines: Ignored
#
# Example:
#   2025-01-01              # Single day holiday
#   2025-01-28~2025-01-31   # Spring Festival (4 days)
#
# Note: Weekends (Saturday & Sunday) are automatically skipped
#       You only need to add national holidays and special days off

